name: This is Salem
description:
There are no words. No air either. But everything moves as if in the wind, as if someone were speaking. Everything is in a frenzy and you can't do anything but stay there. 

No hay palabras. Tampoco hay aire. Pero todo se mueve como por el viento, como si alguien hablara. Todo está en frenesí y no puedes hacer otra cosa que quedarte quiero.
